title: Ми більше ніж я
overview: 10 years of married life is the limit of Nastia and Maks' relationship. Passion and genuine feelings had disappeared between them, but scandals and a mistress appeared. How to resuscitate marriage? It's simple - to move Nastia's soul to Maks, and his spirit to her body. How did that happen? Watch the series "We are more than I am".
